column4: This shiny and well-designed silver horse pendant is crafted of fine sterling silver with high polished finish that can add a little sparkle to your day. The width measures 47mm with a height of 23mm and just the right size to match any casual outfit.

column3: PONY PORTRAIT OXIDIZED STERLING SILVER HEART PENDANT
column4: Simple yet elegant, this exquisite pony image etched in a heart-shaped solid sterling silver pendant is oxidized and buffed to a silver shine. The antique look complements any sporty attire.
